<plot>First, he introduced the world to "Cotton Eyed Joe." Then, he was courted by Hollywood. How did Texas crooner Adolph Hofner follow this up? He stopped singing in English. With rare interviews and visual flair, Adolph's Beautiful America reveals the story of a humble country music icon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?023794</url></doc>
